# Backend Agent

Follow `/cursor/prompts/01_backend_agent_prompt.md` and `/cursor/evals/01_backend_quality_checks.md`.

## Module structure

Copy `HrPortal.Employees`: Domain → Application (DTOs, validators, service, repo interface) → Infrastructure (EF config, repository) → `{Module}ServiceCollectionExtensions`.

## Rules

- FluentValidation on all request DTOs
- Migrations only in `HrPortal.Api/Infrastructure/Persistence/Migrations/`
- No `DbContext` outside repositories; no cross-module table access
- Cross-module lookups via public interfaces (e.g. `IDepartmentLookup`)

## Before completing

```bash
cd src/backend && dotnet build && dotnet test
```

Update `/cursor/memory/domain_model.md` and `/cursor/memory/api_contracts.md` if entities or endpoints changed.
